__e: Hey, let me see your doll for a second.
I thought we were playing dolls and having fun and stuff like that, and all of a sudden your doll is out of control.
Maybe you, me and your dummy could go get a hot beverage.
She had lost her parents and had taken a liking to my doll.
"l won´t need this dolly any more", she said.
And when my dolly was sad it made me sad too.
- She knows the doll is missing.
